      "content": "The Kenyan marathon runner and the Brazilian sportswear vibe sounds cool, but for a luxury watch we really need that \"old money\" or high-society feel. Can you refine the list? Like, instead of athletes, can you give me more specific archetypes for the non-white models so I can tell the client exactly what kind of \"look\" or \"status\" each one brings to the brand?",
